name: APE DAO REMIX! #0021
description: APE DAO REMIX! Project is a collection of NFTs derived from the first 50 BAYC NFTs that were the genesis of APE DAO. Each of the DAO's Apes was remixed by some of the hottest NFT artists in the community. There are 111 editions of each Remix in the collection and each NFT includes membership to the exclusive APE DAO community.
